# Commit template for Linkfy
# Follow convention: <type>(scope): description
#
# Available types:
# feat     - New feature (MINOR version bump)
# fix      - Bug fix (PATCH version bump)  
# chore    - Maintenance, configuration
# docs     - Documentation only
# style    - Formatting, whitespace
# refactor - Code restructuring without functional change
# perf     - Performance improvement
# test     - Tests
#
# Common scopes:
# api        - Changes in server/
# client     - Changes in client/
# extension  - Changes in chrome-addon/
# shared     - Changes in shared/
# auth       - Authentication
# ui         - UI components
# config     - Configuration files
#
# Breaking changes: add ! after type (e.g: feat!:)
# 
# Examples:
# feat(client): add track preview component
# fix(api): resolve spotify timeout issue
# chore(deps): update typescript to v5
# docs: update installation guide
#
# Line 1: max 50 characters, imperative mood, lowercase, no period
# Line 2: empty
# Line 3+: optional detailed description